* [[Ceramic Abstracts]]
* [[Chemical Abstracts Service]]
* [[Cambridge Structural Database]]
* [[Current Contents]]/ Physical, Chemical and Earth Sciences
* [[Inorganic Crystal Structure Database]]
* [[International Nuclear Information System]]
* [[Inspec]]
* [[Metals Abstracts]]/[[METADEX]]
* [[Science Citation Index]]
* [[Scopus]]
}}
According to the ''[[Journal Citation Reports]]'', the journal has a 2017 [[impact factor]] of 3.232.<ref name=WoS>{{cite book |year=2017 |chapter=Journal of Synchrotron Radiation |title=2017 Journal Citation Reports |publisher=[[Thomson Reuters]] |edition=Science |series=[[Web of Science]] |title-link=Journal Citation Reports }}</ref>

